Copa México 1989-90 (Cup Tournament)

Teams were seeded 1-20 based on points at the end of the round 19
in the 1989-90 league:

( 1) Puebla             (11) Irapuato
( 2) America            (12) Ciudad Juarez
( 3) U. de Guadalajara  (13) Santos
( 4) U.N.A.M.           (14) U.A.G.
( 5) Necaxa             (15) U.A.T.
( 6) Morelia            (16) Toluca
( 7) Monterrey          (17) Atlante
( 8) U.A.N.L.           (18) Guadalajara
( 9) Cruz Azul          (19) Veracruz
(10) Atlas              (20) Tampico - Madero

